des: This skill is able to provide: News, Events, Traffic, and a reading of the Arbor Newsletter to University Park, Texas residents.You can also ask about any active emergency alerts, or to read Tweets from the city's Twitter account.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
